overview: The first feature-lenght live performance by Rogério Skylab released in video, Skylab IX chronicles the pinnacle of Skylab's career in a gig that goes through some of his most famous songs. Recorded in September 2008 at Centro Cultural São Paulo. Featuring guest appearances by Maurício Pereira, Marcelo Birck and Löis Lancaster.
title: Skylab IX - Ao Vivo
